label-md font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest opacity-80\">AI Recognition Stats</h3>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"text-[48px] font-bold leading-tight\">99.8%</h2>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm opacity-90\">Model analysis accuracy rate across 12,450 unique industrial parts processed this month.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/20\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between text-label-sm\">\n<span class=\"\">Total Models</span>\n<span class=\"font-bold\">14,289</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between text-label-sm mt-2\">\n<span class=\"\">Avg Processing Time</span>\n<span class=\"font-bold\">1.2s</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Cost Breakdown -->\n<div class=\"col-span-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm\">\n<h3 class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-6\">Cost Breakdown</h3>\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-center h-48 relative\">\n<!-- Semi-donut ring simulation -->\n<div class=\"w-40 h-40 rounded-full border-[16px] border-primary border-r-tertiary border-b-secondary-container\"></div>\n<div class=\"absolute flex flex-col items-center\">\n<span class=\"text-headline-md font-bold text-on-surface\">¥42k</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-sm text-outline\">Avg Cost</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-3 mt-6\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n<span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span>\n<span class=\"text-body-sm text-on-surface\">Material</span>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-bold\">45%</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n<span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-tertiary\"></span>\n<span class=\"text-body-sm text-on-surface\">Machining</span>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-bold\">38%</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n<span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary-container\"></span>\n<span class=\"text-body-sm text-on-surface\">Surface Treatment</span>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-bold\">17%</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Material Usage -->\n<div class=\"col-span-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm\">\n<h3 class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-6\">Material Usage</h3>\n<div class=\"space-y-5\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between text-label-sm mb-1.5\">\n<span class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">Aluminum 6061-T6</span>\n<span class=\"text-outline\">2.4 Tons</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full bg-surface-container-low rounded-full h-2\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 85%\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between text-label-sm mb-1.5\">\n<span class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">Stainless Steel 316L</span>\n<span class=\"text-outline\">1.8 Tons</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full bg-surface-container-low rounded-full h-2\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 65%\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between text-label-sm mb-1.5\">\n<span class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">Nylon PA12</span>\n<span class=\"text-outline\">0.9 Tons</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full bg-surface-container-low rounded-full h-2\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 40%\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between text-label-sm mb-1.5\">\n<span class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">Carbon Steel 1045</span>\n<span class=\"text-outline\">0.7 Tons</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full bg-surface-container-low rounded-full h-2\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 32%\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Process Distribution -->\n<div class=\"col-span-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm\">\n<h3 class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-6\">Process</h3>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2\">precision_manufacturing</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-bold\">58%</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-sm text-outline\">CNC Milling</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2\">layers</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-bold\">22%</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-sm text-outline\">3D Printing</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2\">view_in_ar</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-bold\">12%</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-sm text-outline\">Sheet Metal</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2\">settings_input_component</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-bold\">8%</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-sm text-outline\">Others</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Personal Procurement Visualization (Full Width Row) -->\n<div class=\"col-span-12 glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-8\">\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"text-headline-md font-headline-md text-on-surface\">Personal Procurement</h3>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm text-outline\">Individual spending trends and order lifecycle management for Zhang Wei.</p>\n</div>\n<button class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-label-md\">\n                        View Detailed Report <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">arrow_forward</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n<div class=\"space-y-6\">\n<div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-outline-variant\">\n<p class=\"text-label-sm text-outline mb-1\">Yearly Spend</p>\n<h4 class=\"text-headline-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">¥1,248,000</h4>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-green-600 text-label-sm mt-1\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]\">trending_up</span> +12.5% vs LY\n                            </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-outline-variant\">\n<p class=\"text-label-sm text-outline mb-1\">Open Orders</p>\n<h4 class=\"text-headline-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">24</h4>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-primary text-label-sm mt-1\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]\">schedule</span> 8 Due this week\n                            </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-3 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-bold\">Monthly Expenditure Cycle</span>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2\">\n<span class=\"text-[10px] py-0.5 px-2 bg-surface-container-high rounded\">Forecasted</span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] py-0.5 px-2 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container rounded\">Actual</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-end justify-between h-32 gap-3\">\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-surface-container-low h-[40%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-surface-container-low h-[55%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[70%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[85%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[60%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[90%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[75%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[82%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[68%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[95%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-primary h-[100%] rounded-t-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"fl